==> Which services does the server expose? (reflection)
grpc.health.v1.Health
grpc.reflection.v1.ServerReflection
inventory.v1.InventoryService

==> What methods does InventoryService have?
inventory.v1.InventoryService.GetProduct
inventory.v1.InventoryService.ListProducts
inventory.v1.InventoryService.ProcessOrders
inventory.v1.InventoryService.RecordShipments
inventory.v1.InventoryService.WatchStock

==> Full schema of a method, straight from the server
inventory.v1.InventoryService.GetProduct is a method:
rpc GetProduct ( .inventory.v1.GetProductRequest ) returns ( .inventory.v1.Product );

==> UNARY call (JSON in, JSON out - grpcurl transcodes to protobuf)
{
  "sku": "SKU-0001",
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "description": "Tenkeyless mechanical keyboard with hot-swappable switches",
  "price_cents": "12999",
  "currency": "USD",
  "quantity_available": 87,
  "category": "PRODUCT_CATEGORY_ELECTRONICS",
  "updated_at": "2026-07-08T02:52:15.027625Z"
}

